<section>
<title>Detailed Description</title>

<para>Include &lt;glm/gtx/handed_coordinate_system.hpp&gt; to use the features of this extension.</para>

<para>To know if a set of three basis vectors defines a right or left-handed coordinate system. </para>
</section>
